data.description: Views views views! If you've been looking for secluded mountain living within an hour of downtown Denver, this is the property you've been waiting for! Situated on one acre, this 3,000 square foot mountain home is ready for your customizations. Enjoy gorgeous sunrises off the large deck that has recently been restored for longevity, and relax in the evenings next to the wood burning stove. With a new roof, new sewer line to the septic tank, and restored/sealed siding, this home is ready for it's new owners to enjoy as is, or transform into the ultimate dream home. NO HOA and zoned A-1! You won't find another home in this condition and price up in Coal Creek Canyon! Schedule your showing today, motivated sellers, bring all offers! Assumable VA loan!
